  "title": "Short Video & Live Streaming Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong><br /><br />We are a growing marketing company specializing in advertising services and traffic generation for clients. Due to business expansion, we are looking for motivated individuals to join our team.</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Participate in trade shows and exhibitions to promote the client's brand</li><li>Record short videos and conduct live streaming at events</li><li>Create engaging content to drive traffic and brand exposure</li><li>Handle on-site coordination and basic event setup</li><li>Other ad-hoc content and marketing support tasks</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Experience in short video production and/or live streaming (TikTok, Douyin, YouTube Shorts, or similar platforms)</li><li>Basic spoken Chinese (able to communicate effectively during events in China)</li><li>Willing and able to travel for business (approximately 12–15 trips per year, each trip 3–5 days; about 80% of trips in China)</li><li>Proactive, adaptable, and comfortable working in fast-paced event environments</li></ul><p><strong>What We Offer</strong></p><ul><li>Basic monthly salary: S$4,000 – S$5,000 (depending on experience)</li><li>13-month salary</li><li>Performance-based bonus (according to individual and team results)</li><li>Company-sponsored medical insurance</li><li>Flexible work location (primarily event-based + remote coordination days)</li></ul>",
